"README"
 bj-jedi (Blackjack Jedi)

bj-jedi is a blackjack simulator, trainer, and analyzer.

programs:
boc2: simple standard blackjack odds calculator, +card sensitivity analysis,
	using only approximate methods
bjgrader: interactive blackjack trainer and analyzer (stdio UI)
bjswoc: blackjack switch odds calculator

analysis utilities:
bj-dealer-odds: calculation of dealer's final state spread using various methods

papers:
bj-math.pdf: a detailed and academic text about odds, edge, and strategy calculations in blackjack

